<Body> 
	<Title>背景资料：1952年伦敦烟雾事件</Title>  
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2014-05-04 17:25</ReportTime>  
	<Content> 
		<Paragraph>
			<Sentence> 
				<Event eid="e1">
					<Time tid="t1" type="timeInterval">1952年12月4日至9日</Time>，
					<Location lid="l1">伦敦</Location>
					<Object oid="o1">上空</Object>受
					<Object sid="s1">高压系统</Object>
					<Denoter did="d1" type="action">控制</Denoter>
				</Event>， 
				<Event eid="e2">
					<Object sid="s2">大量工厂</Object>
					<Denoter did="d2" type="operation">生产</Denoter>
				</Event>和 
				<Event eid="e3">
					<Participant sid="s2">居民</Participant>
					<Denoter did="d2" type="operation">燃煤取暖</Denoter>
				</Event>  
				<Event eid="e4">
					<Denoter did="d4" type="action">排出</Denoter>的
					<Object oid="o4" sid="s5">废气</Object>
				</Event>  
				<Event eid="e5">难以
					<Denoter did="d5" type="action" polarity="negative">扩散</Denoter>
				</Event>， 
				<Event eid="e6">
					<Denoter did="d6" type="action">积聚</Denoter>在城市
					<Object oid="o6">上空</Object>
				</Event>。
			</Sentence>  
			<Sentence> 
				<Event eid="e7">
					<Location lid="l7">伦敦城</Location>被黑暗的
					<Object sid="s7">迷雾</Object>所
					<Denoter did="d7" type="action">笼罩</Denoter>
				</Event>，马路上几乎没有车， 
				<Event eid="e8">
					<Participant sid="s8">人们</Participant>小心翼翼地
					<Means type="method">沿着人行道</Means>
					<Denoter did="d8" type="action">摸索前进</Denoter>
				</Event>。
			</Sentence>  
			<Sentence>大街上的电灯在烟雾中若明若暗，犹如黑暗中的点点星光。</Sentence>  
			<Sentence> 
				<Event eid="e9">
					<Time tid="t9" type="timeInterval">直至12月10日</Time>，强劲的
					<Object sid="s9">西风</Object>
					<Denoter did="d9" type="action">吹散了</Denoter>笼罩
					<Location lid="l9">在伦敦上空</Location>的
					<Object oid="o9">恐怖烟雾</Object>
				</Event>。
			</Sentence>
		</Paragraph> 
	</Content>  
